add_rf_device.description:
A 433 MHz device was detected via RF signal:

- **Protocol:** {protocol}
- **Model:** {model}
- **House:** {house}
- **Unit:** {unit}
- **UID:** {device_uid}

Give the device a name and click **Submit** to add it.

For sensors you can also **add to an existing device** (e.g. indoor + outdoor probes of the same weather station) or **replace** an existing sensor (e.g. after battery change). Check **Ignore** to hide it.

[📖 User Guide: Automatic add](https://github.com/R00S/addon-tellstick-local/blob/main/docs/USER_GUIDE.md#51-automatic-add-press-to-discover)

